教育学院毕业。\n\n十七世杜彩霞：女，师专毕业。\n\n十七世杜鲜英：本科毕业，医师。\n\n十七世杜学峰：师专毕业。\n\n十八世杜超：永勤子，大学本科。义马市委工作。\n\n十七世杜卫华：硕士研究生。烟台工作。\n\n十七世杜旭峰：茯苓长子，大学本科，任陕县人行行长，市银监局办公室主任。经济\n\n师，副县级。\n\n十七世杜旭辉：茯苓次子，大学本科，任人民银行渑池县支行行长。\n\n十八世杜山：旭峰子，留学英国。\n\n十七世杜润娜：金铎，女，大学本科，经济师。\n\n十七世杜震：大专，医师。\n\n十八世杜宪：大学本科。\n\n十八世杜志明：本科毕业。\n\n十九世杜清：本科。\n\n十九世杜丽娜：本科。\n\n十九世杜娟：专科。\n\n十九世杜清鹏：大专。\n\n", "isStart": true, "isEnd": true, "images": {"imgs/img_in_image_box_148_497_263_588.jpg": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//ac9f6316-7776-4ed2-9933-814ce45dbfb5/markdown_0/imgs/img_in_image_box_148_497_263_588.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A27%3A24Z%2F-1%2F%2F86f3bc8eb3fcc1793a740e6c8a006bbc6a127f102ea9ae2aba27a60304c0bccf", "imgs/img_in_image_box_148_2645_270_2744.jpg": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//ac9f6316-7776-4ed2-9933-814ce45dbfb5/markdown_0/imgs/img_in_image_box_148_2645_270_2744.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A27%3A24Z%2F-1%2F%2F81ee6a7090cb9a9ce19687ff0aec5a8b8c5bfd5776781db1479cbc4bc9084dae"}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//ac9f6316-7776-4ed2-9933-814ce45dbfb5/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A27%3A26Z%2F-1%2F%2F3c200bd35a73a8de3c796b8e886bca996872410de73939b73f41b67d27814cc6", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//ac9f6316-7776-4ed2-9933-814ce45dbfb5/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A27%3A26Z%2F-1%2F%2F1a185a38af04b65be44d787e77f98fe526d395273fd68cbbfc19eb440ac7a379", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//ac9f6316-7776-4ed2-9933-814ce45dbfb5/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2F